ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Small Business and Tourism of SUZANNE TROTTIER of West Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Nancy M. Laird, whose term has expired.
